videos.headline: L. Jackson pass to C. Hikutini for 28 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Lamar Jackson pass complete to Cole Hikutini for 28 yds to the Clem 1 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Louisville picks off Watson at the goal line
videos.description: Jaire Alexander ends a promising Clemson drive by picking off Deshaun Watson at the goal line preserving the Cardinals' 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Clemson strikes back for 33-yard game-tying TD
videos.description: After throwing a pick at the goal line on their last drive, Deshaun Watson comes right back with a 33-yard touchdown pass to Deon Cain to bring Clemson level at 7-7 with Louisville.

videos.headline: Watson fumbles ball right back to Louisville
videos.description: Deshaun Watson run for 15 yds to the Lvile 39 Deshaun Watson fumbled, recovered by Lvile

videos.headline: Louisville trails for the first time all year after Gallman 24 yard TD run
videos.description: Wayne Gallman run for 24 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Clemson goes to Cain for another big-play TD
videos.description: Clemson makes it three touchdowns in a row, this time a 37-yard strike from Deshaun Watson to Deon Cain to put the Tigers up 21-7 on Louisville.

videos.headline: Jackson takes exception to Ben Boulware tackle
videos.description: Tempers flare after Lamar Jackson is taken to the ground by Clemson LB Ben Boulware

videos.headline: Clemson strikes again right before halftime for 28-10 lead
videos.description: Clemson goes 73 yards in 32 seconds, finishing with a five-yard pass to Artavis Scott for the Tigers' fourth touchdown of the quarter, going up 28-10 right before halftime.

videos.headline: Louisville head coach Bobby Petrino thinks his team needs to get their poise back
videos.description: Louisville head coach Bobby Petrino thinks his team needs to get their poise back

videos.headline: Louisville recovers Leggett fumble
videos.description: Deshaun Watson finds Jordan Leggett on a 15-yard pass, but Leggett fumbles the ball and Louisville recovers for an 18-yard return.

videos.headline: L. Jackson pass,to J. Smith for 29 yds for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Jackson runs in, Louisville down just two
videos.description: After recovering a Clemson fumble, Lamar Jackson guides Louisville down the field and runs in for a one-yard TD and the Cardinals are only down 28-26.

videos.headline: Louisville field goal gives them 19 unanswered 2nd half points and the lead

videos.headline: Clemson back on top after Watson finds Leggett for TD
videos.description: Deshaun Watson finds Jordan Leggett for a 31-yard touchdown to put Clemson back on top. The Tigers take a six-point lead over Louisville after capitalizing on a two-point conversation.

videos.headline: Louisville comes up a yard short on final drive
videos.description: On 4th-and-12, Lamar Jackson finds James Quick, who gets stopped a yard short of the first down, and Louisville falls to Clemson 42-36.
